Feature: Cart Operations\n\n  Scenario: User adds a product to the cart\n    Given the user is on the product page\n    When the user clicks the \"Add to Cart\" button for a product\n    Then the product should be added to the cart\n    And the user should see the cart updated with the added product\n\n  Scenario: User removes a product from the cart\n    Given the user has a product in the cart\n    When the user clicks the \"Remove\" button for the product in the cart\n    Then the product should be removed from the cart\n    And the user should see the cart updated without the removed product